ect<\/strong>: Ellis Maples<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"color: #2eab4d;\"><strong>Year Opened<\/strong>: 1986<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3>Course Rating<\/h3>\n<p style=\"margin-top:35px;\"><div class='one-fourth first'><\/p>\n<p><strong style=\"color: #0d4f82;\">Tee<\/strong><br><span style=\"color: #0d4f82;\"> Blue<\/span><br><span style=\"color: #0d4f82;\">White<\/span><br><span style=\"color: #0d4f82;\">Gold<\/span><br><span style=\"color: #0d4f82;\">Red<\/span><br><span style=\"color: #0d4f82;\">Pink<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #0d4f82;\"><\/div><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #0d4f82;\"><div class='one-fourth'><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #0d4f82;\"><strong>Yards<\/strong><\/span><br><span style=\"color: #0d4f82;\"> 6148<\/span><br><span style=\"color: #0d4f82;\"> 5760<\/span><br><span style=\"color: #0d4f82;\"> 5109<\/span><br><span style=\"color: #0d4f82;\"> 4746<br>3846<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #0d4f82;\"><\/div><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #0d4f82;\"><div class='one-fourth'><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #0d4f82;\"><strong>Men&#8217;s Rating<\/strong><\/span><br><span style=\"color: #0d4f82;\"> 69.7<\/span><br><span style=\"color: #0d4f82;\"> 67.8<\/span><br><span style=\"color: #0d4f82;\"> 64.6<\/span><\/p>\n<span style=\"color: #0d4f82;\"><strong>Ladies Rating<\/strong><\/span>\n<br><span style=\"color: #0d4f82;\"> 75.8<\/span>\n<br><span style=\"color: #0d4f82;\"> 73.5<\/span>\n<br><span style=\"color: #0d4f82;\"> 69.5<\/span>\n<br><span style=\"color: #0d4f82;\"> 68.4<\/span>\n<br><span style=\"color: #0d4f82;\"> 62.6<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #0d4f82;\"><\/div><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #0d4f82;\"><div class='one-fourth'><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #0d4f82;\"><strong>Men&#8217;s Slope<\/strong><\/span><br><span style=\"color: #0d4f82;\"> 125<\/span><br><span style=\"color: #0d4f82;\"> 119<\/span><br><span style=\"color: #0d4f82;\"> 110<\/span><\/p>\n<span s